# nstructions for Neya’s Technical Test

## Overview

The [technical test repo](https://github.com/joinneya/technical-test) contains a very small chat application and an intentionally unfinished AI agent.

The goal is **not** to build a feature-rich app, but to design a **well-behaved AI agent** that helps people find the right group.

Timebox: **~2–3 hours**.

